(2, 'Iloilo City', 'Domestic Tour', '2D1N, 3D2N, 4D3N', '🏝️𝗜𝗟𝗢𝗜𝗟𝗢 𝗖𝗜𝗧𝗬 𝗧𝗢𝗨𝗥 𝘄𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗚𝗮𝗿𝗶𝗻 + 𝗜𝗦𝗟𝗔 𝗚𝗜𝗚𝗔𝗡𝗧𝗘𝗦 𝟯𝗗𝗔𝗬𝗦 𝟮𝗡𝗜𝗚𝗛𝗧𝗦\r\n\r\nPRIVATE TOUR FOR 1 PAX\r\n23,650 x 1 = 23,650 Total\r\n\r\n𝗜𝗻𝗰𝗹𝘂𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀:\r\n✔ Private Tour for 1pax\r\n✔ Pick up and Drop off at Airport\r\n    \"Must be Same Day of the tour\"\r\n     Pick up & proceed to tour \r\n     After tour drop off to airport\r\n✔ 2 Nights Aircon Accommodation \r\n✔ Day 2 & Day 3 Breakfast\r\n✔ FerryMar as Hotel with private CR\r\n✔ Entrance fee at Garin Farm\r\n✔ Driver/Guide, Roro Fee, & Parking Fees\r\n✔ Exclusive Aircondition SUV as transpo for: \r\n- Iloilo City \r\n- Isla Gigantes Transfer \r\n✔ Tour Guide Fees (Isla Gigantes Tour)\r\n✔ Private Island Hopping Tour to Isla Gigantes\r\n✔ Island Environmental fees  at Isla Gigantes\r\n✔ Buffet Lunch with unlimited scallops during Island Hopping at Isla Gigantes\r\n\r\n𝗘𝘅𝗰𝗹𝘂𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀:\r\nχ Other Meals\r\nχ Airfare\r\nχ Hotel pick-up and airport drop-off (outside the proposed itinerary dates).\r\n\r\n𝘾𝙡𝙞𝙘𝙠 𝙝𝙚𝙧𝙚 𝙩𝙤 𝙫𝙞𝙚𝙬 𝙩𝙝𝙚 𝙝𝙤𝙩𝙚𝙡 𝙖𝙘𝙘𝙤𝙢𝙢𝙤𝙙𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣 𝙥𝙝𝙤𝙩𝙤𝙨:\r\nhttps://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1-3AryeDVzFga65dOyEptgG_Hky5nOQoU?usp=drive_link\r\n\r\nThese itinerary will be customized depends on your arrival and departure and which should comes first. Final itinerary will be given after reservation.\r\n\r\nSample Itinerary\r\nDay 1: Pick up at Airport / Check in hotel at 2pm\r\nDay 2: Isla Gigantes \r\nDay 3: Iloilo City Tour | Drop of at Airport/Hotel\r\n\r\n𝗗𝗔𝗬 𝟮 - 𝗜𝗦𝗟𝗔 𝗚𝗜𝗚𝗔𝗡𝗧𝗘𝗦 𝗣𝗥𝗜𝗩𝗔𝗧𝗘 𝗗𝗔𝗬 𝗧𝗢𝗨𝗥\r\n(4:00Am - 4pm)\r\n📍Pulupandan\r\n📍CabugaoGamay\r\n📍Bantigue Sandbar\r\n📍Antonia Beach\r\n📍Mini Boracay\r\n📍Tanke Lagoon\r\nDrop off at hotel\r\n\r\n𝗗𝗔𝗬 𝟯- 𝗜𝗟𝗢𝗜𝗟𝗢 𝗖𝗜𝗧𝗬 𝗗𝗔𝗬 𝗧𝗢𝗨𝗥\r\n(Max of 10hrs - 7:30AM - 4:00PM)\r\nPick up at Hotel /Airport\r\n📍Garin Farm\r\n📍Miag-ao Church\r\n📍Molo Mansion\r\n📍Molo Church\r\n📍Esplanade\r\n📍ILOMOCA\r\n📍Jaro Cathedral\r\n📍Casa Mariquit\r\n📍Festive Walk\r\n📍Megaworld\r\n📍Capitol\r\n📍Pasalubong Center\r\nDrop off at hotel/Airport \r\n\r\n𝗧𝗘𝗥𝗠𝗦 & 𝗖𝗢𝗡𝗗𝗜𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡𝗦:\r\n✹For guaranteed booking, a reservation/downpayent of P2,000 per person is required. The remaining balance should be paid via our bank accounts or GCash at least 3 days before the travel dates. \r\n\r\n✹Strictly no cancellation. Down payment is non-refundable.\r\n\r\n✹ Hotel accommodation is subject to room availability. Availability may change from time to time.\r\n\r\n✹Rates are subject to change without prior notice unless paid.\r\n\r\n✹If guests did not arrive on the scheduled date, a “No Show Penalty” equivalent to the whole package amount will be charged.\r\n\r\n✹Vantrippers Travel and Tours reserve the right to cancel, refund or reschedule any trip under these circumstances:\r\n\r\n✹ If there is a report of typhoon that may compromise the safety of our passengers.\r\n\r\n✹ The itinerary can be changed at land operator’s discretion to best suit the guest interest due to unexpected situations on the ground.\r\n\r\n𝗣𝗟𝗘𝗔𝗦𝗘 𝗕𝗘 𝗔𝗗𝗩𝗜𝗦𝗘𝗗:\r\n-Please note that the rates provided here are not fixed and do not apply during  Special Holidays, Long Weekends, Peak Season, December, and Holy Week. Rates are subject to change without prior notice.\r\n\r\n-Additionally, the rates do not include taxes. If you require a service invoice, an additional 12% VAT will be applied based on the total amount. However, if you only request a carbonized Acknowledgment Receipt, we can issue it free of charge. Please be aware that any shipping costs for receipts will be the responsibility of the client.\r\n\r\nCall us if you have any questions: 📞0976-4764187 or call us here on messenger simply click the phone icon 📞 above on the right side!\r\n\r\n📧 or email us at book@vantripperstravelandtour.com\r\n\r\n🌐Check out our FB Page for more details: https://www.facebook.com/Vantrippers.ph\r\n\r\n📩Shoot us a message: m.me/vantrippers.ph  \r\n\r\nWe are legit Travel Agency with:\r\n✔️Complete and Updated Business Permits\r\n\r\n✔️With Physical Office: Visit us at HMC Building Unit 5 Brooke Side Lane, San Francisco Gen. Trias, Cavite.\r\n\r\n✔️D.O.T Approved Travel Agency with Accreditation: DOT-R4A-TTA-01919-2024 \r\n\r\n✔️Our Bank Accounts with BDO and BPI are all under the name of our Travel Agency: Vantrippers Travel and Tours\r\n\r\n✔️We accept Credit Card Payment thru PayMaya secured Payment Link with 5% bank charge', '1741427699_460827089_964485305717792_1909916109449437663_n.jpg', NULL, NULL, '2025-03-10 06:02:39');
